ther progress of the Pasha Ismael southward of his present position will be successful, there is every reason to believe; and I derive great pleasure from the reflection, that his success will still further augment the glory of the man whom the Sultan del
\hich\af0\dbch\af36\loch\f0 i\hich\af0\dbch\af36\loch\f0 ghts to honor, and who has done so much for the honor of the Mussulmans.
